NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
T.D.E., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
C.C.E., Sr., Defendant. In the Matter of the Guardianship of C.C.-B.E. Jr., C.A.E. and C.G.E., Minors-Respondents. 079007
C-108 Sept. Term 2017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-296/297-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
